replies.body:
I was careful to not use the word "game", as I figured that was probably the case. 

Though I'd argue taking the title "level designer" for anything that isn't a game is by definition incorrect and deliberately intended to confuse. In which case you can probably understand why people attempt to put words in your mouth and speculate based on common understanding of your job title, as opposed to something which might be a bit more representative of your actual responsibilities.

Still my curiosity still remains as strong as ever over all these years as to what it is you're actually doing and will continue to be subtly trolled by you probably for many more years.{{sticker:sg-janna}}
